                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In the early morning of September 15 (Korean time), forces of the United Nations
                    Command successfully launched an amphibious assault against the North
                    Korean-held port of Inchon. This was the first phase of a United Nations
                    offensive to drive the North Korean forces out of the Republic of Korea. For
                    details and references to other sources, see Appleman, <hi rend="italic">South
                        to the Naktong, North to the Yalu</hi>, pages 488 ff.</p>
            </div>
